<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Guard Alvin Robertson of the Milwaukee Bucks was ordered by a San Antonio judge 
to attend a program on spousal abuse and to perform 50 hours of community 
service in connection with a misdemeanor assault charge brought against him by 
his wife. 
</P>
<P>
Robertson, 28, was charged after he allegedly grabbed the hand of his wife, 
Jacquelin, and struck it against a concrete floor last month. 
</P>
