COUNTY; MEDICAL CARE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS; 
SAFETY INSPECTIONS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT 
</P>
