<TEXT>
<P>
Soviets Close Pizza Hut: A dispute over jurisdiction between the Kievsky 
regional council and the Moscow city council has resulted in the closure of one 
of the two Pizza Hut restaurants that opened with great fanfare 10 days ago, a 
restaurant official said. "We apologize to our customers for the temporary 
