</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS -- USSR; PIZZA HUT; JOINT VENTURES; 
BUSINESS CLOSINGS; FAST FOOD INDUSTRY -- USSR; RESTAURANTS -- USSR 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
