grip of Villa Park's Jason Braun during the Griffins' 17-10 victory. ; Photo, 
Villa Park's Ryan Tsui blocks extra-point attempt by Los Alamitos' Eric Wallace 
at the beginning of the second quarter. C14. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
