<DOCID> 281653 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 22, 1990, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
